The '''Yinchorri command center''' was the headquarters of the [[Yinchorri High Command]]. It was located in an underground base on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Uhanayih]]. In [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]] during the [[Yinchorri Uprising]], it was attacked by the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]] in the [[Battle of Uhanayih]].

